//Recipe
//Each section of the mecha may have many parts
//The sections are core, leftArm, rightArm, hips, head
AddRecipeParts core 1 largeCompositeBody 5 SMP_Part_Mat_Armor_Titan 4 Fiber
AddRecipeParts leftArm 1 smallIronArm 1 Fiber
AddRecipeParts rightArm 1 smallIronArm 1 Fiber
AddRecipeParts hips 2 smallIronLeg 2 Fiber
